<center> <h2> Listing alerts </h2> 
   


<br>
<br><br><br>
<style>
table, th, td {
    border: 1px solid grey;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    background-color: white;
}
</style>


<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th> <h3>Alerts </h3> </th>

    </tr>
  </thead>



<tbody>
   <ol>
<% @all_alerts.each do |alert| %>
<tr>
   
    <td> <strong>Descriere: <%= alert.description %> </strong>
    <br>
Votantul cu CNP-ul <%= alert.voter_cnp%>, numele <%= @all_voters.select{|voter| voter.cnp == alert.voter_cnp}.first.last_name %> si prenumele <%= @all_voters.select{|voter| voter.cnp == alert.voter_cnp}.first.first_name%> a votat initial la angajatul din teritoriu <%= alert.user_id%>, cu numele <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.user_id}.first.last_name %> si prenumele <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.user_id}.first.first_name%> de la sectia de votare <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.user_id}.first.voting_section%> la data de <%= (alert.time + 2.hours).strftime('%a, %d %b %Y %H:%M:%S') %>. S-a inregistrat o alerta, conform careia votantul in cauza a incercat sa voteze la o alta sectie, la angajatul din teritoriu <%= alert.current_user_id%>, cu numele <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.current_user_id}.first.last_name %> si prenumele <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.current_user_id}.first.first_name%> de la sectia de votare <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.current_user_id}.first.voting_section%> la data de <%= (alert.created_at + 2.hours).strftime('%a, %d %b %Y %H:%M:%S') %>.

  <br>
<% end %>

</tr>  
  </tbody>
</ol>

</table>


<br>
<h2>
  De investigat - Posibile fraude
</h2>

<h3>
  Votanti
</h3>


<% @alertscnp.each do |alert| %>
   
<p>Votantul cu CNP-ul <%= alert.voter_cnp%>, numele <%= @all_voters.select{|voter| voter.cnp == alert.voter_cnp}.first.last_name %> si prenumele <%= @all_voters.select{|voter| voter.cnp == alert.voter_cnp}.first.first_name%>. </p>


<% end %>
<h3>
  Angajati
</h3>


<% @alertsuser.each do |alert| %>

<p>Angajatul din teritoriu <%= alert.user_id%>, cu numele <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.user_id}.first.last_name %> si prenumele <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.user_id}.first.first_name%> de la sectia de votare <%= @all_users.select{|user| user.id == alert.user_id}.first.voting_section%>.</p>



<% end %>

